commit.message:
demangle.h: #include "ansidecl.h" rather than #include <ansidecl.h>.

	* demangle.h: #include "ansidecl.h" rather than #include <ansidecl.h>.
	* fibheap.h: Likewise.
	* hashtab.h: Likewise.
	* partition.h: Likewise.
	* sort.h: Likewise.
	* splay-tree.h: Likewise.

From-SVN: r54974
